thing to their child.

00:17:20.393 --> 00:17:24.163
[HARUHIME] I incurred my
father's wrath. There was
nothing I could do.

00:17:25.264 --> 00:17:27.767
[HARUHIME] So many things have
happened since then.

00:17:27.867 --> 00:17:32.739
