00:17:51.023 --> 00:17:53.192
Yeah that's... "The
Adventures of Garrard"!

00:17:53.292 --> 00:17:55.194
The one where the queen was
suffering from an illness,

00:17:55.294 --> 00:17:57.163
so he searched for
the grail to cure her!

00:17:57.263 --> 00:17:59.131
Oh wow, you
know of it!

